properties.name: Umbria
properties.description: Posted by BbumbriaUmbria has many beautful places to see. Try first Perugia, Assisi, Spoleto, Orvieto, Todi, Gubbio, and all the small cities such as Montefalco, Bevagna, Spello, Narni, Amelia and much more!

properties.name: Umbria, the green heart of Italy
properties.description: Posted by BbumbriaUmbria is a region in the center of Italy. It\'s known as "green heart of Italy". Why? Well, you should come to better understand it! It has a many cultural and touristic placs to see, such as Assisi, the home town of San Francesco, Perugia, where you can see Etruscan and Roman ruins and the Galleria Nazionale dell\'Umbria, and many small cities where you can relax and enjoy umbrian food and ospitality!
